<Base title="Privacy Policy — North Lane Pick" description="Privacy policy for North Lane Pick.">
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>
    This Privacy Policy explains how North Lane Pick ("we", "us") handles
    information when you visit this website.
  </p>

  <h2>Information we collect</h2>
  <p>
    We do not ask you to create an account or submit personal information to read
    this site. Like most websites, basic, non-identifying technical data (such as
    browser type and pages visited) may be collected automatically by our hosting
    provider and analytics tools to help us understand traffic.
  </p>

  <h2>Affiliate links</h2>
  <p>
    This site contains affiliate links to Amazon. When you click them, Amazon may
    use cookies to track that the visit came from our site so that we can be
    credited for qualifying purchases. Your activity on Amazon is governed by
    Amazon's own privacy policy. See our
    <a href="/affiliate-disclosure">affiliate disclosure</a> for more.
  </p>

  <h2>Third-party services</h2>
  <p>
    We use Amazon's Associates Program and may use standard web analytics. These
    third parties have their own privacy policies governing the data they
    collect.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    If you have questions about this policy, please reach out through the contact
    method listed on our <a href="/about">About</a> page.
  </p>

  <p><em>This policy may be updated from time to time.</em></p>
</Base>
